soldHouses.Remarks: Sleek Contemporary View Home! Rare flat lot. Dramatic entry with 2 sty living room. Large glass windows and sliding pocket doors throughout. Open kitchen w/ white Carrera marble, stainless steel appliances, b'fast bar, dining area, family room, and wet bar. Dual primary suites, balcony, walk-in closets, big city views, huge glass shower, separate spa tub, dual vanities and full dry sauna. Outdoor living room, fire pit, pool/spa, outdoor dining w/ pergola, bbq, sports/recreation area, 3 car garage, parking for 6. Spectacular home with a premium flat lot! Easy to show.
soldHouses.RemarksForSchema: Sleek Contemporary View Home! Rare flat lot.

soldHouses.Remarks: The perfect blend of warmth and contemporary living in this exceptional residence epitomizes the quintessential California lifestyle. Nestled behind a row of stately olive trees and private gates is a south-facing home bathed in an abundance of natural light from every space. The expansive home spans nearly 4,000 square feet, featuring 4 bedrooms and 4 baths. Soaring ceilings and open-concept living space opens to the chef's kitchen adorned with impeccable finishes and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. Glass accordion doors connect to the outside, revealing a resort-like backyard with a zero-edge infinity pool, spa, charming atrium and fire pit, perfect for entertaining. The voluminous primary suite is complete with 14 foot ceilings, a walk-in closet, balcony, black out curtains, and a spa-inspired bath with a 5-function smart shower. Two additional large en-suite guest bedrooms and a laundry room complete the upper level. To complete this remarkable residence is state-of-the-art smart home technology including keyless and fingerprint entry, an elaborate security camera system, a surround-sound speaker system, as well as dual-zoned AC with NEST thermostats. The two-car garage is outfitted with a modern built-ins and an EV charge station, offering the perfect synergy of sustainable living and modern convenience.
soldHouses.RemarksForSchema: The perfect blend of warmth and contemporary living in this exceptional residence epitomizes the quintessential California lifestyle.

soldHouses.Remarks: This tasteful Spanish residence is located in one of West Hollywood's most desirable pockets; just minutes away from the city's best shopping, eateries and entertainment of Melrose Avenue. The home offers 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms plus a bonus room that can be converted into a 4th bedroom, den or home office. The main living areas boasts an open floor-plan with gleaming wood floors, a dining area with French Doors that opens to a gorgeous patio that is perfect for al fresco dining, entertaining and living the SoCal lifestyle. The property also features an attached 1 + 1 guest unit with full bathroom, kitchen and laundry that can be rented out for additional income or used as a separate work space or for a live in relative/staff member. The front yard is gated, there is a quaint rear grassy yard and a separate side yard. Detached 2 car garage. Offers due 5/2 at 12 Noon.
soldHouses.RemarksForSchema: This tasteful Spanish residence is located in one of West Hollywood's most desirable pockets; just minutes away from the city's best shopping, eateries and entertainment of Melrose Avenue.

soldHouses.Remarks: Recently renovated Spanish modern in Leimert Park. The home spans 2,918 square feet of luxury and privacy, boasting 4-beds, 3.5-baths. Inside, light-filled rooms with exposed ceiling beams, create a sophisticated atmosphere where relaxation comes effortlessly. The thoughtful floor plan invites you to move through the dining room with a designer chandelier into the chef's kitchen with stainless steel appliances, and a grand island perfect for gatherings. The primary suite is its own retreat with a walk-in closet and en-suite bath featuring a lavish soaking tub and shower.Every detail is curated for the most discerning buyer. Enjoy the full-grown Ficus trees which offer privacy and create a serene oasis. A privacy fence around the perimeter of the residence ensures the utmost seclusion and the 3kw solar panels marry luxury with eco-consciousness.
soldHouses.RemarksForSchema: Recently renovated Spanish modern in Leimert Park.

soldHouses.Remarks: Seller says "bring us any reasonable offer"! Nestled in the heart of Beverly Hills, on a beautiful tree-lined street, this exquisite residence at 339 North Palm Drive, Unit 104, offers a rare blend of sophistication and luxury. This light and bright condominium offers an expansive 2-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home (Den could easily be converted to a 3rd bedroom) that spans an impressive 2762 square feet, providing an unparalleled living experience. Upon entering the lobby, an elevator whisks you to this exclusive mid-rise abode, greeted by a stunning interior that exudes elegance. The residence features many amenities, including a garage with 24-hour valet parking and assigned parking for your convenience. Enjoy the abundant pool, spa, and standard media/recreation room, perfect for entertaining guests. Entering through double doors, the home boasts a security system, ensuring peace of mind, and two separate balconies, while pet-friendly policies welcome your furry companions. A well-appointed kitchen with a pantry and wet bar in the den makes this all a culinary enthusiast's dream. The sweeping living room has a fireplace, two gigantic walk-in closets, a bathroom with double sinks, a sunken bathtub, and a large stall shower. The in-unit washer/dryer offers added convenience. Revel in the comfort of air conditioning and ample storage, alongside the indulgence of huge walk-in closets in each generously proportioned bedroom. Embrace the opportunity to make this unrivaled residence your own and relish in the grandeur of Beverly Hills living. With its prime location, this property presents a rare chance to embrace the epitome of luxury living. Please take the opportunity to make this your own and experience the allure of Beverly Hills at its finest.

soldHouses.Remarks: Nestled in the heart of the iconic Beverly Hills proper, 116 N Swall Dr #401 offers the rare opportunity to own a residence in one of the most coveted and prestigious cities in the world. This exquisite high-floor unit, brimming with luxury and sophistication, is situated in an elegant boutique building, allowing residents to enjoy a private, elevated lifestyle. Spanning an impressive 1,942 square feet, this spacious 2-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence includes a large den with dual closets, perfect for a home office, bedroom, or additional living space. The bright, open floor plan is complemented by the convenience of in-unit laundry and side-by-side parking with electric vehicle charging. The building also features a communal pool and sauna, providing a resort-like experience right at home. With its top-floor location, the unit enjoys an abundance of natural light and peaceful, sweeping views of the surrounding neighborhood. Don't miss the opportunity to own a piece of Beverly Hills legacy.

soldHouses.Remarks: What an incredible price! In a category of its own, and the only Golden Age condominium tower available in West Hollywood: A 4th floor residence in the historic Granville, providing character, privacy and security.... the classic Manhattan life.... just moments from the famed Sunset Strip, from boutiques to groceries to cafes and clubs. Features: flexible floorplan with formal entry, large living room with wonderful daylight pouring in from oversized windows, 2 bedrooms (one currently used as a den), 1 classic-style bathroom with separate tub and shower, formal dining room floor-to-ceiling built-in shelves (which could be used as a den or study), large separate kitchen with marble counters, gas stove and stainless steel appliances, refinished wood floors, new paint, high ceilings, walk-in closet, crown molding, inside laundry and AC. Multiple, bright exposures to the west and east, offering sunrise and sunset City views which extend all the way to Downtown LA. This sought-after building, in a coveted neighborhood, is located in the heart of West Hollywood and offers doorman, professional management, wonderful rear garden retreat and Mills Act qualification, which can grant significant savings on property taxes. HOA dues are $1,456/month and include building amenities, dog run, water/sewer/trash and 1 secure parking space. Own a piece of history!

soldHouses.Remarks: Beautifully updated 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath condo with 24 hour concierge service in the highly coveted Marie Antoinette in the Wilshire Corridor! Enjoy quiet privacy and ample sunshine in this rear corner unit with views of the residential Westwood neighborhood. You will love the high ceilings and large windows throughout. Two bedrooms offer generous space for bedroom furniture and large closet storage as well. The third bedroom is a perfect space for an office or bonus room. Enjoy sunsets from your oversized terrace, perfect for taking meals alfresco or just relaxing with a book. The unit includes in-unit washer and dryer, ample storage, two parking spaces and many recent updates! The building is FULL SERVICE with 24 hour concierge, security, valet parking, plenty of guest parking and doorman. HOA includes water, power, gas, trash and sewage (along with staff, housekeeping and maintenance of common areas). Amazing location close to great restaurants, shops and more.
